{"tid":2076121,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李昇基逼問SJ銀赫：認識TWICE嗎？2人一起偷看神秘片","createTime":"2020-06-23T09:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:04:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d79459d177cd027f7e935ab0fb14d57e4fbc1d3f","tid":2076121,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"節目《家師父一體》最新一集中，班底李昇基、梁世炯、申成祿、金東炫、車銀優各自請來好友擔任嘉賓，SJ成員銀赫與李昇基交情甚篤，卻被梁世炯虧：「這兩年來也沒聽你說過！」質疑他們的友誼，銀赫為了證明，爆料對方「不為人知的祕密」，說他們一起看過「某些東西」，就連喜歡TWICE的事情也再被拿出來討論。<br />\n<br />\n銀赫爆料好友祕密：「要是說出這個的話...人們不知道的李昇基！」嚇壞對方回：「你不是也一起看了？」銀赫仍刻意維持神祕感，李昇基無奈表示：「你幹嘛非要講成好像有什麼一樣？你再這樣我要打給利特了！」而李昇基是眾所周知的TWICE狂粉，銀赫說他跟軍中長官一樣，一見面劈頭就問：「你跟TWICE熟嗎？」一番話讓李昇基嚇到跳起，讓銀赫大笑說：「他也是男人啊！」<br />\n<br />\n李昇基跟銀赫認識超過10年，但主持《家師父》2年多期間，李昇基都未跟大家聊起對方，梁世炯質疑他們友情，2人綜藝魂爆發，笑說：「剛剛來到錄影現場，我們重新互存手機號碼了。」十分爆笑。"},{"pid":"e21ddd8408c6cc8c504a370af3692a6ed0a4c6ce","tid":2076121,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x6Dk1u.E_y8xudgk.tFHNA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/f232e25290528f7e0d63fd7c76fdbdf2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx6Dk1u.E_y8xudgk.tFHNA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2Ff232e25290528f7e0d63fd7c76fdbdf2&h=edc9824a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼銀赫（右）說李昇基問他認不認識TWICE。（圖／翻攝SBS、銀赫IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7FXH4RM85d7rPIeEl.GO.A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/128e7e709b7f1d33180d91bcaccf3e8f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7FXH4RM85d7rPIeEl.GO.A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F128e7e709b7f1d33180d91bcaccf3e8f&h=3